#include<iostream>
#include<math.h>
typedef unsigned long long int ul;
using namespace std;
int main()
{
    ul a,b;
    double phi=.208987;
    double r5=2.236067;
    cin>>a;
    cin>>b;
    while( a!=0 || b!=0)
    {
           ul x,y;
           x=(ul)((log10(r5*a))/(phi));
           y=(ul)((log10(r5*b))/(phi));
           cout<<(y-x)<<"\n";
           cin>>a;
           cin>>b;
           }
           return 0;
}
